		<title>Vanishing Stories</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/ThePassiveVoice/~3/YAknbqGsvLY/</link>
		<comments>http://www.thepassivevoice.com/01/2015/vanishing-stories/#comments</comments>
